      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2021R2) is commercially licensed and version-controlled; simulation scripts retained under institutional repository with checksums.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is a commercially supported release subject to vendor QA processes. Version control logs confirm no unauthorized modifications were made to solver inputs or post-processing scripts during the study period."
